      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it a dependable choice for a daily driver. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear and tear consistent with its age, the car remains structurally sound and mechanically solid. It is ready for the road and offers a comfortable, worry-free driving experience for its next owner.",
