      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a reliable choice for daily transportation. While the engine and transmission are functional, there are visible signs of wear including minor exterior scratches and some fading in the interior upholstery. It has been regularly maintained, though it may soon require attention for minor items like brake pad replacement and a suspension tune-up. This is an honest, drivable car for someone looking for a budget-friendly option without needing immediate major repairs.",
