    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that ensures a mirror-like finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip. Inside, the cabin remains an oasis of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear, still carrying that distinct 'new car' aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. With exceptionally low mileage and a history of gentle use, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the moment it rolled off the assembly line. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
